""" Test to check that get_session_request returns expected dict when session_id is empty."""
test_params = {'method': 'POST', 'session_id': '', 'metric': '',
    'auth_token': AUTH_TOKEN, 'params': 'test_params', 'data':
    '{"test_data": "test_data"}'}
expected = {'method': 'POST', 'url': BASE_URL + VERSION + SESSION_SUFFIX,
    'attributes': {'headers': NO_METRIC_HEADERS, 'params': 'test_params',
    'data': '{"test_data": "test_data"}'}}
self.director = RequestDirector(**test_params)
actual = self.director.get_session_request()
self.assertEqual(expected, actual)
